SITE ADVSEARCH {
plugin org.drftpd.commands.indexmanager
class IndexManager
method doAdvSearch
perms *
help Searches for files and diretories in the index w/ advanced filters.
help.specific ${command} <options>
help.specific Options: -user <user> -group <group>
help.specific Options: -type <f/file|d/dir> -slaves <slave[,slave,..]>
help.specific Options: -age <start timestamp> <end timestamp>
help.specific Options: -size <min size> <max size>
help.specific Options: -name <word> [word ..]
help.specific Name MUST be the last option in the command.
help.specific Multipe options are allowed. If multiple options are given a file/dir must match all options.
}

